Beautifully and tastefully renovated canal house with deep, sunny urban garden. Located on a beautiful part of the canal district east. The property is very spacious and functionally laid-out and has surprising details. 260 sqm on five floors.

I live downstairs in the basement with my own entrance and bathroom seperataly from visitors. You can always call me if you need something and I will arrange it as soon as possible.

metro to Central Station around the corner. From airport to Central Station 15 min by train.
